Ma yella yiwen deg-wen ixḍeb tilemẓit, iḥar ur yezmir ara ad yeṛǧu ibɣa ad yezweǧ, mačči d ddnub ma yella yezweǧ.
A wen-d-iniɣ tideț : di mkul amkan n ddunit anda ara yețțubecceṛ lexbaṛ-agi n lxiṛ, a d-țmektayen tameṭṭut-agi d wayen akka texdem.
Kunwi s imasiḥiyen xḍut i zzna, i wayen ur neṣfi ara, i ṭṭmeɛ ; ayagi meṛṛa ur ilaq ara a d-ițwabdar gar-awen ulamma d abdar ;
Lameɛna llan ɣuṛ-es kra yemdanen ur sneǧsen ara llebsa-nsen ; ad ilin yid-i s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara, qṛib a nili d ugur ula i yiwen seg imecṭuḥen-agi.
A lḥukkam d lecyux n wat Isṛail ! Imi ɣef lxiṛ i nexdem i wergaz-agi aɛiban d wamek i geḥla i ɣ-d-testeqsayem ass-agi,
Ar ass-a qquṛen iqeṛṛay-nsen, gguman ad fehmen ; imi leḥjab-nni ur yekkis ara m'ara d-ɣṛen di tira iqedsen n ṭṭlam, iwakken ad rren lqima i lmut.
Tenɛețțab aṭas ger ifassen n ṭṭeba, texṣeṛ ayen akk i tesɛa, meɛna ur teḥli ara, terna tenṭer akteṛ.
tella dinna yiwet n tqeḍɛit n yilfan i gkessen dinna.
Lɛeskeṛ n igenwan lsan llebsa tamellalt n lfina yețfeǧǧiǧen yerna ttabaɛen-t ɣef yiɛewdiwen imellalen.
Di leǧwahi-nni, tella yiwet n tqeḍɛit tameqqrant n yilfan i gkessen dinna.
M'ara ț-țerren ɣer wakal tețțuɣal d ulac, meɛna m'ara d-teḥyu, a d-teḥyu s ccan d ameqqran. M'ara ț-țerren ɣer wakal teffeɣ-iț tezmert, m'ara d-teḥyu a d-teḥyu s lǧehd d ameqqran.
Ma yella iḍlem-ik yiwen, tedduklem di sin ɣer wexxam n ccṛeɛ, ɣiwel msefham kečč yid-es deg ubrid, m'ulac axṣim-ik a k-yawi ɣer lḥakem, lḥakem a k-yefk i wɛessas, aɛessas-nni, a k-yerr ɣer lḥebs.
Ma d kunwi, medden meṛṛa ẓran tḍuɛem Sidi Ṛebbi, d ayen i yi-sfeṛḥen. ?menniɣ aț-țxedmem ayen yelhan s ṣṣwab, ur s-țaǧǧat ara abrid i cceṛ.
Lameɛna wwḍen ɣer yiwen wemkan n ṛṛmel iwumi d-izzi lebḥeṛ ; rran ɣer dinna lbabuṛ-nni, lǧiha n zdat teḥṣel di ṛṛmel teḥbes ma d lǧiha n deffir tebda tețṛuẓu si lqewwa n lemwaji.
Di lweqt-nni, yiwen lmelk n Sidi Ṛebbi iweḥḥa-d i Sidna Ibṛahim, Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin i gellan di temdint n Yillu.
Ass-nni ilaq wid ara yilin di temdint n Lquds ad ffɣen, wid ara yilin di lexla ur keččmen ara ɣer temdint, wid ara yilin di tmurt n Yahuda ad rewlen ɣer idurar.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ?
Lameɛna wwḍen ɣer yiwen wemkan n ṛṛmel iwumi d-izzi lebḥeṛ ; rran ɣer dinna lbabuṛ-nni, lǧiha n zdat teḥṣel di ṛṛmel teḥbes ma d lǧiha n deffir tebda tețṛuẓu si lqewwa n lemwaji.
Meɛna imdanen-agi țɛicin am lmal n lexla, lhan kan i ṣṣyada, ur țxemmimen ara, reggmen ayen ur ssinen ; ad ɣlin di tesraft n ddnubat nsen, ad mmuṛdsen akken ițmuṛdus lmal.
Mkul Tafaska n izimer n leslak Bilaṭus yețserriḥ-ed i yiwen umeḥbus.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Lameɛna ur tɛeṭṭel ara tekker-ed yiwet n tbuciḍant iwumi qqaṛen Erakilun i d-ikkan seg idurar n tegzirt-nni.
Llan wid i d-ițxebbiṛen s wayen i d-ițțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, ilaq ad nadin ɣef lecyux n wat Isṛail ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail, ara seg wid yesselmaden lekdeb.
Tafaska n izimer n leslak yeɣli-d deg wass n westeɛfu. Tameddit n wass uqbel ass n westeɛfu, lecyux n wat Isṛail ur bɣin ara ad ǧǧen lǧețțat-nni ɣef yimidagen di leɛwaceṛ. Ṛuḥen ad ssutren i Bilaṭus a sen-ṛẓen iḍaṛṛen i widak-nni yețwasemmṛen ; iwakken ad kksen lǧețțat-nsen.
Leɛqiṛa tis snat, tețțunefk-as tezmert a s-tefk ṛṛuḥ i lmeṣnuɛ n leɛqiṛa-nni tamezwarut, iwakken lmeṣnuɛ-nni ad yizmir a d-yenṭeq, yerna ad ineɣ meṛṛa wid yugin a t-ɛebbden.
Imi nuggad a ɣ-yawi waḍu ɣer leryuf iweɛṛen n tmurt n Libya, ncudd lbabuṛ s imurar ; nerna nṣubb-ed lbac-nni s wayes i t-yețțawi waḍu, neǧǧa iman-nneɣ a ɣ-yawi ɣer wanda yebɣa.
Mmi-s n bunadem asm'ara d-yas, ula d nețța i geqqimen seg wedrum n Galasya, wid iwumi d-iṣubben si leɛṛac n igenwan ɣer wannect-agi, ad qqimen mebɛid,
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, ur tețțen ara alamma uɣen luḍu. ?ṭfen daɣen deg waṭas n lɛaddat nniḍen : tarda n yeqbac, n tbuqalin, akk-d lḥilat meṛṛa n n nnḥas.
Ițemcabi ɣer uɛeqqa n uxerḍel. M'ara t-nezreɛ, d nețța i d aɛeqqa amecṭuḥ meṛṛa ger zzerriɛat n ddunit.
Teččam lḥeqq n wid imegren igran-nwen, slet-asen i wigi ițcetkin ɣef lbaṭel-nwen, Sidi Ṛebbi Bab n tezmert yesla-d i leɛyaḍ-nsen.
Leɛqiṛa tețwaṭṭef nețțat d nnbi nni n lekdeb i gxeddmen lbeṛhanat seddaw n lḥekma-s, s wayes ikellex imdanen meṛṛa yețwaḍebɛen s ṭṭabeɛ n leɛqiṛa yerna țseǧǧiden.
Yezmer lḥal ad yili yiwen seg watmaten neɣ si tyessetmatin xuṣṣen di llebsa, lluẓen ur sɛin ara ayen ara ččen ;
tella dinna lḥila n ddheb i deg sseṛɣayen lebxuṛ akk-d usenduq n leɛqed iṛuccen s ddheb.
ilaq a sen-terrem tikmamin i yimawen-nsen. Skarayen lhul deg yexxamen m'ara sselmaden ayen ur nlaq ara, iwakken ad rebḥen leḥṛam.
